abstract: Google and Yahoo said Wednesday that they notified the Justice Department before the start of a joint search advertising test that could lead to a broader partnership between the two companies. The two Internet giants also said they have answered questions from Justice Department officials about their arrangement.

abstract: When I zoom in on a photo using the Google Earth program, the image is sometimes blurry. Is there a way to fix this?
snippet: When I zoom in on a photo using the Google Earth program, the image is sometimes blurry. Is there a way to fix this?
lead_paragraph: Q. When I zoom in on a photo using the Google Earth program, the image is sometimes blurry. Is there a way to fix this, or are there other similar services available that have better picture quality?
